Interface StringConcatFactory.StringConcatItem

Enclosing class:
StringConcatFactory
public static interface StringConcatFactory.StringConcatItem
StringConcatItem is a preview API of the Java platform.
Programs can only use StringConcatItem when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
Implementations of this class provide information necessary to assist StringConcatFactory perform optimal addition.
